trans-unit.source: Supports the page parser in building a template and the child controls it contains.
trans-unit.target: Støtter siden parseren bygge en mal og barnet Kontroller den inneholder.

trans-unit.source: To use a custom TemplateBuilder class for a control, create a custom <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder> for the control, and then return the custom TemplateBuilder control from the <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.GetChildControlType%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil bruke en egendefinert TemplateBuilder klasse for en kontroll, kan du opprette en egendefinert <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder>for kontrollen, og deretter returnere egendefinerte TemplateBuilder kontrollere fra den <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.GetChildControlType%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.GetChildControlType%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.TemplateBuilder"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.TemplateBuilder"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Used during design time to build the template and its child controls.
trans-unit.target: Brukt under utformingen for å bygge malen og de underordnede-kontrollene.

trans-unit.source: A reference to the instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.TemplateBuilder"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: En referanse til forekomsten av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.TemplateBuilder"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Called by the parser to inform the builder that the parsing of the control's opening and closing tags is complete.
trans-unit.target: Kalles av parseren å informere verktøyet at analyse av kontrollens innledende og avsluttende koder er fullført.

trans-unit.source: Initializes the template builder when a Web request is made.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer malen builder når en forespørsel utføres.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.TemplateParser"></xref> responsible for parsing the control.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Web.UI.TemplateParser"> </xref> ansvarlig for å analysere kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder"></xref> responsible for building the control.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder"> </xref> ansvarlig for å bygge kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Type> assigned to the control that the builder will create.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Type>tilordnet til kontrollen som oppretter verktøyet.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: The name of the tag to build.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på koden til å bygge.

trans-unit.source: This allows the builder to support multiple tag types.
trans-unit.target: Dette gjør at verktøyet til å støtte flere typer i koden.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.ID*> assigned to the control.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.ID*>tilordnet kontrollen.</xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.ID*>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.IDictionary> that holds all the specified tag attributes.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Collections.IDictionary>som inneholder alle attributtene angitte koden.</xref:System.Collections.IDictionary>

trans-unit.source: Defines the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Control"></xref> object that child controls and templates belong to in design time.
trans-unit.target: Definerer den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Control"> </xref> objekt at underordnede kontroller og maler tilhører under utformingen.

trans-unit.source: The InstantiateIn method is required when implementing the <xref:System.Web.UI.ITemplate> interface.
trans-unit.target: Metoden InstantiateIn kreves når implementering av <xref:System.Web.UI.ITemplate>grensesnittet.</xref:System.Web.UI.ITemplate>

trans-unit.source: The InstantiateIn method is used only in design time.
trans-unit.target: Metoden InstantiateIn brukes bare under utformingen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.Control"></xref> to contain the instances of controls from the inline template.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Control"> </xref> skal inneholde forekomster av kontroller fra innebygde malen.

trans-unit.source: Determines if the control builder needs to get its inner text.
trans-unit.target: Bestemmer om kontrollen builder trenger å hente teksten.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.TemplateBuilder.SetTagInnerText%2A> method needs to be called when we are in design time.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.TemplateBuilder.SetTagInnerText%2A>metoden må kalles når vi er under utformingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.TemplateBuilder.SetTagInnerText%2A>

trans-unit.source: The NeedsTagInnerText method returns the value of the <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.InDesigner%2A> property of the base <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder> class.
trans-unit.target: Metoden NeedsTagInnerText returnerer verdien for <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.InDesigner%2A>egenskapen for base <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder>klasse.</xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder> </xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.InDesigner%2A>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the control builder needs to get its inner text.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis verktøyet kontrollen skal hente teksten.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Saves the inner text of the template tag.
trans-unit.target: Lagrer interne teksten i malen-koden.

trans-unit.source: The SetTagInnerText method overrides the base class's <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.SetTagInnerText%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method and sets the value of the <xref:System.Web.UI.TemplateBuilder.Text%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Metoden SetTagInnerText overstyrer basisklassen <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.SetTagInnerText%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden og angir verdien for den <xref:System.Web.UI.TemplateBuilder.Text%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.TemplateBuilder.Text%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.SetTagInnerText%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The inner text of the template.
trans-unit.target: Indre teksten for malen.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the text between the opening and closing tags of the template.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir teksten mellom innledende og avsluttende koder for malen.

trans-unit.source: The Text property is used by the designer to specify or determine the text that appears between the opening and closing tags of the template.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen Text brukes av designer for å angi eller fastslå teksten som vises mellom innledende og avsluttende koder av malen.

trans-unit.source: The text that appears between the opening and closing tags of the template.
trans-unit.target: Teksten som vises mellom innledende og avsluttende koder for malen.
